  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnimatedEntity
    An Entity with animations
    Entity
    An object or character that can rendered with a Sprite at a specified location
    GameState
    One of the game's "states" that has unique render and tick methods
    Map
    Collection of "sectors" that make up a map, which is like a level or world
    MapSector
    Specific part, or area, of a map
    MapSectorDefinition
    A collection of map tiles used for defining a map sector
    MapTile
    A "tile" that is rendered within a map sector
    StaticEntity
    An entity that does have not any animations
